      .fw-bold.mb-1 Use our checklist

      ul.list-unstyled
        li.d-flex.align-item-center
          span.me-2.bi.bi-check-lg
          span The lesson is divided into meaningful blocks with subheadings
        li.d-flex.align-item-center
          span.me-2.bi.bi-check-lg
          span The subtitles are worded to reflect the subthemes of the lesson
        li.d-flex.align-item-center
          span.me-2.bi.bi-check-lg
          span The rule “One paragraph is one thought” is followed
        li
          .d-flex.align-item-center.mb-2
            span.me-2.bi.bi-check-lg
            span The topic of the lesson is revealed consistently:

          ul.ms-2 type="disc"
            li
              p.mb-2 “From the familiar to the unfamiliar”
            li
              p.mb-2 “From simple to complex”
            li
              p.mb-2 “From the general to the particular”

        li.d-flex.align-item-center
          span.me-2.bi.bi-check-lg
          span The introduction explains how the lesson is structured, what topics are covered, and why these topics are important
        li.d-flex.align-item-center
          span.me-2.bi.bi-check-lg
          span The conclusion summarizes and lists the key points

