        .fw-bold.mb-1 Paragraph and sentence structure

        ul type="disc"
          li
            p.mb-2 No monotonous passages with the same length of sentences
          li
            p.mb-2 No paragraphs with hidden convoluted thoughts (“worth mentioning”, “take note”)
          li
            p.mb-2 No sentences with hidden action (verbal nouns)
          li
